data.description: In the heart of lovely University City, just minutes from Clayton and Highways is this spacious ranch. With 2000 square feet on the main level and several finished rooms in the lower this house has tons of space. The house is a mixture of classic elegance with beautiful arched doorways and wood floors and casual coziness in the family room and kitchen. As you walk in the formal living room is to the left with a cozy wood burning fireplace  and the dining room is to the right. There is a pocket door in dining room with access to the kitchen. With the family room, enclosed sunroom and large bedrooms you have a wonderful family home. The original bathroom tile is beautiful. The main bathroom offers a walk in tub! The lower level offers a huge rec space, bar and another finished room that could be a sleeping area or office with a 3rd bathroom. With a nice level yard and 2 car garage, sitting on a beautiful street within this walkable community your home can be your oasis. "As-Is" sale.
